ZH: 我们需要修剪树枝，以保持树木的健康。
EN: We need to prune the branches to maintain the health of the tree.

ZH: 我每年夏天都会修剪花园里的灌木。
EN: I prune the shrubs in my garden every summer.

ZH: 你需要用修剪刀把植物修剪整齐。
EN: You need to trim the plants neatly with pruning shears.

ZH: 植物生长过快，需要进行修剪。
EN: The plants are growing too fast, they need to be pruned.

ZH: 做好修剪工作，可以改善草坪的外观。
EN: Proper pruning can enhance the appearance of the lawn.

ZH: 别忘了修剪蔓延的绳草，以避免其过度生长。
EN: Don't forget to trim the spreading rope grass to prevent it from growing excessively.

ZH: 我们雇了专业园艺师来修剪花坛中的花草。
EN: We hired a professional gardener to prune the flowers in the flowerbed.

ZH: 在修剪树枝时要注意不要损害树木的健康。
EN: Be careful not to damage the health of the tree when pruning branches.

ZH: 修剪可以帮助控制植物的形状和尺寸。
EN: Pruning can help control the shape and size of plants.

ZH: 这些玫瑰花太长了，需要修剪一下。
EN: These roses are too long, they need to be pruned.

ZH: 他们正在修剪芒果树以促进果实的生长。
EN: They are pruning the mango tree to promote fruit growth.

ZH: 这些丛林植物已经过度生长，需要及时修剪。
EN: These jungle plants have overgrown, they need to be pruned in time.

ZH: 为了维持园林的美观，需要定期修剪草地边缘的植物。
EN: To maintain the beauty of the garden, it is necessary to regularly trim the plants along the edge of the lawn.

ZH: 修剪不仅可以改善植物的形状，还可以增加透光性。
EN: Pruning can not only improve the shape of plants but also increase light penetration.

ZH: 当心修剪时，小心不要剪断植物的主干。
EN: Be careful not to cut off the main trunk of the plant when pruning.

ZH: 花店里的花束都经过修剪，以保持花朵的鲜艳。
EN: The bouquets in the flower shop are pruned to keep the flowers vibrant.

ZH: 这些树枝太密集了，需要修剪掉一些。
EN: These branches are too dense, some of them need to be pruned.

ZH: 在修剪前，先检查工具是否锋利。
EN: Before pruning, check if the tools are sharp.

ZH: 修剪树枝的最佳时间是在冬季休眠期。
EN: The best time to prune branches is during the winter dormant period.

ZH: 修剪这些花朵将帮助它们更好地开花。
EN: Pruning these flowers will help them bloom better.
